entries.m_whatthehell: Not us!  Don't shoot at us, we're innocent!
entries.a_whatthehell: Unit under attack!  Take cover and return fire!
entries.a_victory: Rebel uprising pacified.  No further activity detected in this area.  Good job team.
entries.m_victory: I'm still alive?  I AM STILL ALIVE!!!  Take THAT you Imperial goons!
entries.a_insult4: You were sufficiently warned.  Squad, arrest these men.
entries.m_insult3_response: There will be no surrender for the Rebellion!
entries.a_insult3: We have no desire to use force, but we will if you do not surrender immediately.
entries.m_insult2_response: Is that a threat?  We haven't done anything.  We refuse to be arrested by thugs!
entries.a_insult2: Cooperate with my directive and you will not be harmed.
entries.m_insult1_response: We aren't criminals!  We did nothing illegal!
entries.a_insult1: Rebel recidivists: surrender your weapons and put your hands above your heads.
